CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 5, 1958, pg. 5 reads: "4. Dan-Dee Pretzel Company chose three lovely ladies to show three of their tasty products. Left to right: Mabel B. Mills, Arlene Thompson and Betty Moore.  Representatives Catherine Delvin, Fanny Lucas, Herb Shork, and Truman J. Fisher are not shown"
TitMainTitle: Mabel B. Mills, Arlene Thompson, and Betty Moore holding bags of Dan Dee products, in Dan Dee Pretzel and Potato Chips booth, for the 1958 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair, Syria Mosque
